Label: Infrastructure Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of infrastructure

Label: Transport Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of transport infrastructure

Label: Aviation Infrastructure Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of aviation transport infrastructure

Label: Road Infrastructure Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of road transport infrastructure

Label: Road Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of roads as a transport infrastructure

Label: Road Traffic Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of road traffic

Label: Road Safety Monitoring
Definition: Purposes associated with management of road safety

Label: Road Accident Monitoring
Definition: Purposes associated with monitoring of accidents on roads

Label: Road Condition Monitoring
Definition: Purposes associated with monitoring of road conditions, including weather conditions for safety

Label: Road Pedestrian Safety Monitoring
Definition: Purposes associated with monitoring of conditions, pedestrians, and traffic for safety related to use of roads for pedestrians

Label: Road School Zone Safety Monitoring
Definition: Purposes associated with monitoring of conditions, pedestrians, and traffic for safety in an area nearby or including a school or other similar institutes

Label: Road Maintenance Scheduling
Definition: Purposes associated with scheduling and managing road maintainence

Label: Road Research Development
Definition: Purposes associated with management of research and development for road infrastructure, including planning changes and new infrastructure, analysing traffic and accident patterns, and environmental impact analysis

Label: Road Infrastructure Planning
Definition: Purposes associated with planning road infrastructure

Label: Road Traffic Analysis
Definition: Purposes associated with analysis of road traffic with the goal of researching and developing improvements to road infrastructure

Label: Road Accident Analysis
Definition: Purposes associated with analysis of accidens with the goal of researching and developing improvements to road infrastructure

Label: Road Environmental Impact Analysis
Definition: Purposes associated with conducting environmental impact analysis regarding use and development of road infrastructure

Label: Road Emergency Response Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of emergency response and other safety activities in relation to emergencies in use of road transport infrastructure

Label: Road Emergency Scene Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of the scene during an accident or other emergencies in use of road transport infrastructure

Label: Road Emergency Route Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of routes used for emergency response or managing traffic in response to an emergency response in use of road transport infrastructure

Label: Road Toll Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of tolls and other forms of fees for use of road infrastructure

Label: Road Toll Collection
Definition: Purposes associated with collection of tolls and other forms of fees for use of road transport infrastructure

Label: Rail Transport Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of rail transport infrastructure

Label: Critical Infrastructure Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of infrastructure considered essential or critical for functioning of society and economy as defined by a government or a legislation

Label: Critical Energy Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of critical energy infrastructure and services

Label: Critical Electricity Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of critical electric energy infrastructure and services

Label: Critical Gas Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of critical gas energy infrastructure and services

Label: Critical Water Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of critical water infrastructure and services

Label: Critical Heating Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of critical heating infrastructure and services

Label: Critical Communication Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of critical communications infrastructure and services

Label: Critical Emergency Response Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of emergency response services such as fire fighters and paramedics considered as part of critical infrastructure

Label: Critical Emergency Response Eligibility Assessment
Definition: Purposes associated with assessment of eligibility to dispatch and use emergency response services such as fire fighters and paramedics considered as part of critical infrastructure

Label: Critical Emergency Response Triage
Definition: Purposes associated with prioritisation and other triage procedures to dispatch and use emergency response services such as fire fighters and paramedics considered as part of critical infrastructure

Label: Critical Emergency Response Dispatch Management
Definition: Purposes associated with identifying routes and other dispatch related activities for emergency response services such as fire fighters and paramedics considered as part of critical infrastructure

Label: Critical Emergency Response Communication Management
Definition: Purposes associated with communications involved to request and use emergency response services such as fire fighters and paramedics considered as part of critical infrastructure

Label: Critical Waste Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of waste collection and management considered as part of critical infrastructure

Label: Critical Digital Infrastructure Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of digital infrastructure considered as part of critical infrastructure

Label: Public Transport Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of public transport services

Label: Public Transport Service Provision
Definition: Purposes associated with provision of public transport services

Label: Public Transport Ticket Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of ticketing and other forms of documentation enabling use of public transport services

Label: Public Transport Complaint Management
Definition: Purposes associated with collection, resolution, and analysis of complaints in relation to use of public transport services

Label: Public Transport Safety Management
Definition: Purposes associated with management of safety in use of public transport services, such as through deployment of CCTV cameras in buses or on public transport premises

Label: Public Transport Fraud Management
Definition: Purposes associated with detection, resolution, and analysis of fraud in use of public transport services

Label: Public Transport Research Development
Definition: Purposes associated with research and development activities in relation to public transport services

Label: Public Transport Performance Analysis
Definition: Purposes associated with analysis of performance and other characteristics  with the goal of identifying and making improvements related to public transport services

Label: Public Transport Passenger Flow Analysis
Definition: Purposes associated with analysis of passenger movements in relation to use of public transport services, such as for identifying which areas are most busy on specific days

Label: Public Transport Demand Forecasting
Definition: Purposes associated with predicting demand in relation to public transport services
